                    <msContents>
                        <summary/>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7226AynatBarya">Prayer against the evil eye, Bāryā, Legewon, Šotalāy and
          for pregnant women</title>
                            <note>Containing the legend of Susǝnyos.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ዓይነተ፡ ባርያ፡ ወሌጌዎን፡ ወሾተላይ፡ በእንተ፡ አሰስሎ፡ ደዌ፡ ዘዓቢይ፡ 
                                ወዘንዑስ፡ ወይበቍዕ፡ አዲ፡ ለብእሲ፡ ወለብእሲት፡ ወሚመ፡ ለአእሩግ፡ ወለደቂቅ፡ <sic resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ወይበእቍዕ፡</sic> ለሕሙማን፡ 
                                ወለሕያዋን፡ ወአዲ፡ ለብእሲት፡ ጽንስት፡ ታጽሕፍ፡ ወትሰቅሎ፡ ውስተ፡ ቤታ፡ ወውስተ፡ ውሉዳ፡ ወክሳዳ፡ ከመ፡ ይልሐቁ፡ ደቂቃ፡ 
                                <supplied reason="undefined" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ዘ</supplied>ልፈ፡ ጸሎቱ፡ ወበረከቱ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ሱስንዮስ፡ 
                                <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ወሀሎ፡ ፩ብእሲ፡ ዘስሙ፡ ሱስንዮስ፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7231AynatBarya">Prayer against ʿaynat, the evil eye of Bāryā, and for
          stopping vaginal haemorrhage</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ዓይነት፡ ወአይነተ፡ ባርያ፡ መርግዔ፡ ደም፡ አፍሊስ፡ ሊስ፡ መላሊስ፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1878Marbab">Marbabta Salomon</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ማዕሰረ፡ አጋንንት፡ መርበብተ፡ ሰሎሞን፡ ዘረበቦሙ፡ ለአጋንንት፡ ከመ፡ 
                                መርበበ፡ ዓሣ፡ ዘባሕር፡ እንዘ፡ ይብል፡ ሰዳቃኤል፡ አደታኤል፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6492PPFanuel">Prayer for binding devils with the first stanza of the Malkǝʾa Fānuʾel (Salām to Fānuʾel)</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ጸሎተ፡ ማዕሰረ፡ አጋንንት፡ ሰላም፡ ለተፈጥሮትከ፡ ምስለ፡ መላእክት፡ ሕቡረ፡ እንዘ፡ ኢትከውን፡
                                ቅድመ፡ ወእንዘ፡ ኢትዴኀር፡ ድኅረ፡ ሰዳዴ፡ ሰይጣናት፡ ፋኑኤል፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7233PrColic">Ṣalot baʾǝnta qurṣat wa-wǝgʿāt Dask</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ቁርጸት፡ ወውግዓት፡ ደስክ፡ <gap reason="illegible"/></incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                    </msContents>
